.eslintcache

# Scratch/verification scripts and screenshots from local debugging
# sessions — never meant to be committed. Root-anchored so it can't catch
# legitimate underscore-prefixed files elsewhere (e.g. public/_headers).
/_*.mjs
/_*.png
/_*.log
*_tmp.js
*_tmp.mjs

# Ignore all markdown files except README.md
*.md
!README.md
